      <item>
        <title>This is a post about partner apps</title>
        <description>&lt;h2 id=&quot;getting-started&quot;&gt;Getting started&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The purpose of this post is two fold - 1.)  set up  Partner Application in Validic and 2.) use the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/validic/validic&quot;&gt;Validic Ruby Gem&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;install-the-gem&quot;&gt;Install the gem&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can add the gem to your Gemfile&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;gem&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;validic&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;then run &lt;code&gt;bundle install&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;credentials&quot;&gt;Credentials&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The first step in connecting to Validic is to to have your organization credentials.  If you don’t have those please contact &lt;a href=&quot;&amp;#109;&amp;#097;&amp;#105;&amp;#108;&amp;#116;&amp;#111;:&amp;#115;&amp;#117;&amp;#112;&amp;#112;&amp;#111;&amp;#114;&amp;#116;&amp;#064;&amp;#118;&amp;#097;&amp;#108;&amp;#105;&amp;#100;&amp;#105;&amp;#099;&amp;#046;&amp;#099;&amp;#111;&amp;#109;&quot;&gt;&amp;#115;&amp;#117;&amp;#112;&amp;#112;&amp;#111;&amp;#114;&amp;#116;&amp;#064;&amp;#118;&amp;#097;&amp;#108;&amp;#105;&amp;#100;&amp;#105;&amp;#099;&amp;#046;&amp;#099;&amp;#111;&amp;#109;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you’re using a rails app we recommend storing your organization credentials into environment variables using something like &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/bkeepers/dotenv&quot;&gt;dotenv-rails.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;gem-initializer--set-up&quot;&gt;Gem Initializer &amp;amp; Set up&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We recommend setting up an initializer for the gem so your calls automatically contain your organizaton’s credentials.  In rails that would look like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;Validic&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;configure&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;api_url&lt;/span&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;https://api.validic.com&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;api_version&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;v1&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;organization_id&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;ENV&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;VALIDIC_ORG_ID&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;access_token&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;ENV&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;VALIDIC_ACCESS_TOKEN&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Subsequently this requires you create a &lt;code&gt;.env&lt;/code&gt; file with your credentials:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-ruby&quot; data-lang=&quot;ruby&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;VALIDIC_ORG_ID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;YOUR_ORG_ID_HERE&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;VALIDIC_ACCESS_TOKEN&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

